[![](https://dev.azure.com/lycantropos/wagyu/_apis/build/status/lycantropos.wagyu?branchName=master)](https://dev.azure.com/lycantropos/wagyu/_build/latest?definitionId=28&branchName=master "Azure Pipelines")
